**Problems:** HashMap is NOT thread-safe — concurrent reads/writes cause ConcurrentModificationException or corruption; containsKey + put is not atomic — two threads may both fetch and put (race condition); Field reassignment in refresh() is not atomic with lastRefresh update; No TTL or max size — cache grows unbounded; Route objects may be mutable — shared across threads without protection

